title: Trey Saddler
text:
I am currently a data scientist in the Toxicoinformatics Group of the Predictive Toxicology Branch in the Division of Translational Toxicology at NIEHS (whew…).
I made a YouTube video about Cytoscape that got a lot of views and I would like to get back to making more videos. I have written a few articles a while ago, and have been on some scientific publications.

title: Quarto Gallery
text:
I profess my love for Quarto at every opportunity. Here are some reasons why I think Quarto is great:

Quarto is open source with a GPL-2 license.
Multiple output formats in a single project

All of the built in Pandoc formats (e.g. HTML, PDF, MS Word, Revealjs, ePub, etc.)

Works with R, Python, Shiny
